beer.beer_name: One Brew Nation DDH Hazy Pale Ale
beer.beer_description:
Big on hops but low on bitterness, this contemporary pale ale is loaded with oats for a soft pillowy mouth feel.
Double dry hopped with Vic Secret, Mosiac and Sabro hops that emphasize aroma and fruity flavours.
In addition we've infused one of NOMAD's favourite ingredients, rainforest lime to add a nice zesty flavour. It's got Hygge written all over it.
